OL,5, Doubts have been cast on a claim by    
OL,6, Boris Johnson that the sudden sacking  
OL,7, of 800 workers by P&O Ferries may have 
OL,8, broken UK employment law.              
OL,10,FThe prime minister told the Commons the
OL,11,Ffirm could face fines "running into    
OL,12,Fmillions of pounds" if found guilty.   
OL,14,FBut the Department for Transport later 
OL,15,Facknowledged that there had been a     
OL,16,Fchange in the law Mr Johnson quoted.   
OL,18,FIt came as the boss of P&O Ferries     
OL,19,Fapologised for the mass sacking, saying
OL,20,Fhe understood the "anger and shock".   
